                            <h6 class="text-uppercase fw-bold mb-4">
                                Kontakt
                            </h6>
                            <p><i class="fa fa-home me-3"></i> Rr. George W. Bush, 1001, Tirane</p>
                            <p>
                                <i class="fa fa-envelope me-3"></i>
                                e3computer@yahoo.com
